#lokeshkanagaraj #leo #vijay #lokeshexclusive #lokeshinterview #leoupdate #vikram #kamalhassan #lcu #tamilcinema #cinuelagam

Exclusive Interview & Decoding with Director Lokesh Kanagaraj on his recently released LEO Movie. Leo stars Vijay, Sanjay Dutt, Arjun, Trisha, Gautham Vasudev Menon, Mysskin, Madonna Sebastian, George Maryan, Mansoor Ali Khan, Priya Anand and Mathew Thomas. snippet.title: SPICY CHICKEN WINGS | Hot & Sweet Chicken Recipe Cooking In Village | Spicy Honey Chicken Wings Fry
snippet.description: Today in our village, we cook sweet and spicy chicken wings recipe! We first fried the chicken wings then we made it smokey chicken by keeping it on smoke. We made Hot and Sweet chicken sauce by using Honey and Poprica. Before adding sauce, the chicken wings are so crispy then it is tasty!

snippet.title: Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Leo | Vijay | Trisha | Part 1
snippet.description:

08:41 - 09:40 - What does Loki believe is the truth of Leo?  
09:41 - 10:54  - What is Loki's favourite thing about the Leo flashback
10:55 - 12:00 - Is Loki really constrained by fans 
12:01 - 16:16 - What does it take for young directors like Loki to work with superstars
16:17 - 20:40 - How does Loki see the audience's fixation on box-office numbers
20:41 - 24:38 - Who does Loki think is the villain of Leo?

25:44 - 28:56 - Is Leo a good person or a bad person? 
28:57 - 32.30 - Is Loki glorifying the bad guy in Leo?

33:25 - 37:58 - How does Loki work with his writing room?

snippet.title: Emiway x Savlon Swasth India ‚Äì HAATH DHONA COOL HAI #HandwashLegend ft. The Dharavi Dream Project
snippet.description:
This Iconic Hip-Hop move üëèüèº is now the HANDWASHING Move!
Now after the hack, comes the track!

The track aims to make washing hands with Handwash or Soap cool in the minds of children, keeping them healthy and safe from various illnesses.

Let‚Äôs all wash our hands and become a #HandwashLegend.
___

ITC's Savlon Swasth India Mission - one of the largest school programmes of its kind, is committed to seeding hand hygiene habits in over 85 lakh school children, through continuous awareness and engagement activities.  
___

The Dharavi Dream Project After School of Hip-Hop is a non-profit organisation based in Mumbai. Through various educational programmes, mentorships and community engagement initiatives, it supports children living in Dharavi, Mumbai which today is known for its culturally vibrant hip-hop talent.

#HandwashingForAll #SavlonSwasthIndiaMission
___

Audio Credits:
Song :- HAATH DHONA COOL HAI 
Artist / Lyrics : EmiwayBantai

The track aims to make washing hands with Handwash or Soap cool in the minds of children, keeping them healthy and safe from various illnesses.

Let‚Äôs all wash our hands and become a #HandwashLegend.
___

ITC's Savlon Swasth India Mission - one of the largest school programmes of its kind, is committed to seeding hand hygiene habits in over 85 lakh school children, through continuous awareness and engagement activities.  
___

The Dharavi Dream Project After School of Hip-Hop is a non-profit organisation based in Mumbai. Through various educational programmes, mentorships and community engagement initiatives, it supports children living in Dharavi, Mumbai which today is known for its culturally vibrant hip-hop talent.

#HandwashingForAll #SavlonSwasthIndiaMission

snippet.title: PART 2 Leo Post-release Lokesh Kanagaraj Interview with Sudhir Srinivasan | Leo | Vijay | Trisha
snippet.description:
In this spoiler-filled interaction with Sudhir Srinivasan, #LokeshKanagaraj talks about all things #Leo, bringing #Vijay into the LCU, and more 

This is the SECOND part of the interaction

00:00 - 5:22 - Including History of Violence, what are the other inspirations in Loki's films

05:23 - 07:00 - How did Loki sketch the husband-wife equation in Leo

07:01 - 09:44 - How did the hyena come into the Loki Universe

09:45 - 12:08 - What does Loki think of how people connect the hyena metaphor and other layers of Leo 

12:09 - 14:23 - What elevated Loki's cinematic knowledge

14:24 - 17:48 - What does Loki think of the audience understanding? 

17:49 - 19:37 - What are the plans for the hyena in the LCU? 

19:38 - 20:49 - Will Loki attempt the horror genre? 

20:50 - 23.58 - How does Loki zero in on the retro songs in his films? 

23:59 - 26:16 - How does Loki create an atmosphere for usage of these songs? 

26:17 - 27:20 - What inspired Loki to make that badass Vijay intro card?

27:21 - 28:11 - Why does Loki believe second time is the charm? 

28:12 - 28:38 - Loki on finally bringing Mansoor Ali Khan into the LCU

28:39 - 29:57 - What were the steps Loki took to ensure Parthiban's body adapted to the war scars?
 
29:58 - 32:16 - How important is Anirudh to Loki's films? 

32:17 - 34:27 - What were the various contributions of Anirudh to LEO? 

34:28 - 36:14 - How does Loki work with Anbariv to get the fight choreography on point in Leo? 

36:15 - 37:35 - Does Loki think that the stunts got a bit generic in certain scenes in the second half? 

37:36 - 39:24 - What was the most satisfying response Loki got post the release of Leo? What was his biggest takeaway? 

39:25 - 41:10 - Loki opens up on the LCU Routemap
 
41:11 - 43:23 - Loki signs off by talking about his next biggie,  Thalaivar 171

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/xpresscinema/

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS! Manchester United 0-3 Manchester City | Haaland (2) and Foden Goals!
snippet.description:
City turned in a masterful display to beat Manchester United 3-0 with the best performance so far this season.

Erling Haaland set the Blues on the way with a first-half penalty that was scant reward for the dominance showed.

The Norwegian headed home his second just after half-time before setting up Phil Foden for a late third.

It was no more than the Treble winners deserved after what was a stunning 90 minutes against our cross-city rivals.

Adda247, India's largest vernacular Exam preparation company founded in 2010. Adda247 provides well curated course content & teaching by top faculties of industry for all types of Exam preparations, i.e., Govt jobs, IIT, Medical, State Exams, etc.

Rate Us On IMDB: https://www.imdb.com/title/tt29424187/

Life mein hamesha aapki jeet hi ye possible nahi lekin aap har baar jee jaan se koshish karen ye possible hai. Shiv life ki aankhon mein aankhen daal ke challange accept karta hai aur ek baar phir SSC naam ke pahad par chadne ke liye poori jaan laga deta hai. SSC sir akele hi Khanna ko galat aur apne teaching method ko sahi sabit karne ke struggle mein lage hain. 
Sari duniya ki nazar in dono par hi tiki hai. Kya iss baar himmat ki jeet hogi?

snippet.title: Takeshi‚Äôs Castle - Official Trailer | @BBKiVines | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video Presents
Takeshi‚Äôs Castle - Official Trailer
Directed by Masato Inui
Starring Bhuvan Bam, Beat Takeshi, Osamu Shitara (BANANAMAN), Yuki Himura (BANANAMAN), Shinya Ueda (CREAM STEW), Naomi Watanabe, Ennosuke Ichikawa, Hayato Tani, Subaru Kimura.

Official Release Date November 2, 2023 on Prime Video.

About:
Bhuvan Bam lends his distinctive voice and unique humor as commentator in the brand-new season of Takeshi's Castle. Classic games are making a comeback with new and terrifying obstacles emerging one after another. The lord of the castle, Beat Takeshi, entrusts Bananaman to protect it. Subaru Kimura is the attack force‚Äôs new leader. The elite team gathers to bring down the revived Takeshi‚Äôs Castle.

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows‚Äîall with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ‚Çπ1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video‚Äôs exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ‚Çπ599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination ‚Äì Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent ‚Äì no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting‚ÄØprimevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Mannat Murad Episode 10 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by PEL - 30th October 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Presented by PEL

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

Written by: Nadia Akhtar

Pankaj and Shreya meet a scientist in the jungle who is trapped on the Island. The Tribal People of the Island agreed to help ACP Pradyuman and his team. Abhijeet and Tarika rush to the Island to save their team. Will Team CID find out the truth? To know more, watch this thrilling episode of CID.

Show Cast & Characters: 
‚Ä¢ Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
‚Ä¢ Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
‚Ä¢ Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
‚Ä¢ Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya

‚Ä¢ Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
‚Ä¢ Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1006

#CID #‡§∏‡•Ä‡§Ü‡§à‡§°‡•Ä #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID

About CID:
-----------------
Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.
